<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="permission-n">permission <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pə'mɪʃn/    美 /pər'mɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>许可；准许：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>ask permission</strong>
请求许可</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He entered the room <strong>without permission</strong>. 
他未经许可就进了房间。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>permission to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Give yourself permission to rest when you’re tired.
当你疲倦的时候要让自己休息。</p><footer>2010 安徽</footer></div></div>